summary: I am the infant in this picture.  The toddler is my sister Heather, and the woman holding both of us is my great-grandmother Kay, who I don’t think I have any real memories of.  My mom posted this photo on Facebook and I went into Photoshop to clean it up a bit...
title: Almost Certainly the Earliest Photo Of Me
